ting%20capabilities%20and%20speed.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESovereign%20clouds%20ensure%20data%20is%20stored%20locally%2C%20aiding%20compliance%20and%20national%20security.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAI%20infrastructure's%20uneven%20global%20distribution%20prompts%20nations%20to%20boost%20local%20capacity.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20our%20online%20work%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-nvidia-cloud-ai-anthropic-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehappens%20in%20the%20cloud%3C%2Fa%3E%20these%20days%2C%20though%20we%20likely%20don't%20know%20where%20the%20computing%20is%20actually%20happening.%20The%20location%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-data-center-demand-nvidia-databank-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edata%20center%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20houses%20our%20spreadsheets%20and%20shopping%20lists%20doesn't%20matter%20much%20to%20most%20of%20us%20until%20it%20does.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20age%20of%20AI%2C%20where%20computations%20are%20becoming%20more%20complex%20by%20the%20day%2C%20some%20nations%20are%20looking%20to%20make%20sure%20some%20of%20that%20power%20is%20within%20their%20borders.%20It's%20good%20business%2C%20but%20it's%20also%20a%20matter%20of%20pride%2C%20practicality%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-sam-altman-infrastructure-artificial-intelligence-data-centers-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enational%20security.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVultr%20is%20a%20cloud%20service%20provider%20and%20data%20center%20operator%20founded%20in%202014.%20The%20company%20started%20buying%20Nvidia%20GPUs%20in%202021%2C%20getting%20to%20the%20AI%20cloud%20computing%20business%20earlier%20than%20most.%20It%20operates%20data%20centers%20globally%2C%20with%20both%20traditional%20computing%20and%20AI%20servers%20for%20public%20cloud%20clients%2C%20along%20with%20companies%20and%20countries%20that%20want%20their%20own%20private%20clouds.%20CEO%20J.J.%20Kardwell%20describes%20the%20company%20as%20the%20largest%20privately-held%20cloud%20computing%20platform%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20large%20global%20footprint%2C%20with%20more%20than%2030%20data%20centers%20on%20six%20continents%2C%20helps%20with%20computing%20speed%2C%20especially%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-competition-sambanova-groq-cerebras-show-faster-inference-speed-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20inference%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20also%20makes%20the%20Vultr%20boss%20well-positioned%20to%20explain%20a%20phrase%20frequently%20on%20the%20lips%20of%20AI%20luminaries%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-ceo-jensen-huang-countries-need-own-ai-systems-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENvidia%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang%3A%3C%2Fa%3E%20sovereign%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20Q%26amp%3BA%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20clarity%20and%20length.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBI%3A%20What%20is%20a%20sovereign%20cloud%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESovereign%20cloud%20is%20the%20delivery%20of%20cloud%20infrastructure%20as%20a%20service%2C%20typically%20inside%20a%20country.%20It%20guarantees%20data%20is%20stored%20locally%2C%20which%20ensures%20it's%20used%20strictly%20for%20the%20intended%20purposes%20and%20not%20transferred%20outside%20of%20national%20borders%20without%20explicit%20authorization.%20That's%20the%20essence%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20higher%20levels%20of%20sovereignty%20involve%20no%20communication%2C%20no%20information%20whatsoever%2C%20even%20at%20a%20control%20plane%20level%2C%20passing%20outside%20of%20a%20country.%20Every%20single%20interaction%2C%20even%20with%20a%20platform%2C%20happens%20in-country.%20This%20helps%20ensure%20data%20sovereignty%2C%20data%20residency%2C%20data%20governance%2C%20and%20compliance%20with%20local%20privacy%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBI%3A%20If%20most%20companies%20simply%20rent%20computing%20capacity%20from%20a%20cloud%20provider%2C%20why%20would%20they%20care%20where%20the%20data%20centers%20are%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20cases%2C%20it's%20actual%20compliance%20with%20the%20law.%20For%20example%2C%20let's%20say%20it%20was%20a%20patient's%20medical%20records%2C%20personally%20identifiable%20information%2C%20or%20other%20sensitive%20data.%20They%20may%20have%20a%20compliance%20obligation%20regarding%20where%20they%20can%20store%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20is%20that%20the%20lowest%20level%20of%20risk%20is%20if%20the%20chain%20of%20custody%20can%20be%20documented%20from%20end%20to%20end.%20So%20keeping%20data%20in-country%20and%20in%20a%20sovereign%20cloud%20enables%20the%20highest%20levels%20of%20accountability%20and%20avoids%20transferring%20data%20across%20international%20networks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBI%3A%20How%20does%20a%20sovereign%20cloud%20work%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20true%20technological%20independence%2C%20you%20can%20deliver%20it%20with%20essentially%20an%20air%20gap%20deployment%20and%20a%20dedicated%20control%20plane%20where%20the%20customer%20is%20completely%20untethered%20from%20any%20other%20data%20centers%20or%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20doesn't%20necessarily%20require%20interactions%20with%20data%20from%20many%20sources.%20Many%20training%20jobs%20are%20specific%20data%20sets%20that%20can%20be%20loaded%20onto%20a%20network%20in%20a%20sovereign%20deployment.%20And%20everything%20can%20quite%20easily%20be%20executed%20in-country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20many%20countries%20realize%20that%20some%20of%20the%20most%20important%20applications%20of%20AI%20are%20around%20matters%20of%20national%20security%2C%20critical%20industries%2C%20and%20citizen%20data%2C%20where%20their%20local%20laws%20around%20consumer%20data%20and%20privacy%20may%20be%20very%2C%20very%20different%20from%20those%20in%20other%20countries.%20So%20it's%20quite%20important%20to%20them%20to%20be%20able%20to%20ensure%20for%20their%20citizens%20that%20anything%20that's%20being%20done%2C%20with%20AI%20is%20being%20done%20within%20the%20confines%20of%20the%20country%20and%20in%20compliance%20with%20their%20own%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBI%3A%20What%20do%20people%20mean%20when%20they%20use%20the%20term%20%26quot%3Bsovereign%20AI%26quot%3B%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20focused%20on%20capacity%20in%20a%20specific%20country%2C%20and%20typically%20they're%20talking%20about%20capacity%20sponsored%20by%20the%20government%2C%20whether%20it's%20at%20a%20state%20or%20federal%20level%20within%20that%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20challenges%2C%20or%20inequities%2C%20is%20the%20very%20uneven%20distribution%20of%20AI%20infrastructure%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EObviously%2C%20people%20are%20well%20aware%20of%20the%20transformative%20impact%20that%20AI%20can%20have%20across%20so%20many%20industries%2C%20but%20the%20infrastructure%20itself%20to%20perform%20that%20work%2C%20train%20models%2C%20and%20support%20inference%20is%20very%20unevenly%20distributed%20globally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20countries%20are%20realizing%20that%20if%20they%20don't%20take%20an%20active%20role%20at%20the%20government%20level%20in%20helping%20sponsor%2C%20encourage%2C%20and%20incentivize%20the%20deployment%20of%20infrastructure%20locally%2C%20their%20businesses%20and%20populations%20will%20have%20less%20access%20to%20that%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20definition%2C%20large%20language%20models%20are%20specific%20to%20a%20language.%20And%20the%20biggest%20portions%20of%20early%20innovation%20were%20done%20in%20US%20English.%20Only%20recently%20we're%20seeing%20the%20globalization%20of%20many%20of%20these%20models.%20You%20can't%20train%20on%20a%20US%20body%20of%20data%2C%20for%20example%2C%20for%20legal%20documentation%20then%20do%20simple%20translation%20into%20other%20languages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EObviously%2C%20you'd%20miss%20local%20conventions%20of%20law%20and%20language%2C%20and%20therefore%2C%20translations%20are%20not%20enough.%20You'd%20actually%20need%20to%20do%20training%20on%20local%20models%2C%20on%20local%20bodies%20of%20data.%20Every%20major%20language%20economy%20in%20the%20world%20wants%20to%20benefit%20from%20AI%2C%20yet%20the%20resource%20is%20not%20available%20proportionately%20to%20where%20the%20population%20or%20even%20the%20GDP%20of%20the%20world%20is%2C%20right%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBI%3A%20AI%20computing%20is%20extremely%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-data-centers-us-power-grid-gpu-nvidia-cerebras-amazon-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3Eenergy%20intensive%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20and%20concerns%20about%20the%20US%20grid%20abound.%20Can%20you%20speak%20to%20how%20those%20dynamics%20are%20changing%20where%20data%20centers%20might%20be%20built%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20significant%20growing%20power%20consumption%20of%20AI%20infrastructure%20and%20the%20importance%20of%20its%20efficient%20delivery%2C%20we%20will%20increasingly%20see%20capacity%20building%20in%20global%20markets%20that%20have%20a%20comparative%20advantage%20in%20supporting%20lower-cost%20data%20center%20capacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20a%20strategic%20partnership%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatacenternews.asia%2Fstory%2Fvultr-singtel-enhance-cloud-gpu-capacity-in-southeast-asia%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESingtel%20in%20Singapore%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20if%20you%20look%20at%20the%20way%20that%20they're%20building%20across%20the%20region%2C%20they're%20bringing%20up%20massive%20capacity%20in%20markets%20like%20Malaysia%20and%20others%20where%20we'll%20be%20able%20to%20very%20efficiently%20serve%20the%20region%20and%20much%20of%20the%20world%20where%20you%20see%20more%20efficient%20power%20and%20operating%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2