nister%20also%20said%2C%20has%20an%20important%20role%20in%20ensuring%20the%20security%20of%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20Region%20-%20an%20issue%20red-flagged%20by%20many%20within%20the%20Indian%20government%20after%20President%20Mohamed%20Muizzu%20-%20seen%20as%20a%20'pro-China%20leader%20-%20won%20last%20year's%20election%20on%20an%20'India%20out'%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBe%20it%20essential%20commodities%2C%20vaccines%20during%20Covid%2C%20or%20drinking%20water...%20we%20have%20played%20a%20good%20neighbour%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20India%20had%20also%20inaugurated%20an%20airport%20and%20handed%20over%20700%20social%20housing%20units%2C%20and%20plans%20to%20support%20construction%20of%20a%20new%20port.%20Referring%20to%20the%20drinking%20water%20project%20now%20operational%20on%2028%20Maldivian%20islands%2C%20he%20said%20over%2030%2C000%20people%20would%20now%20get%20clean%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20Maldives%20also%20discussed%20the%20opening%20of%20consulates%20in%20Addu%20and%20Bengaluru%2C%20the%20PM%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Modi's%20comments%20came%20after%20he%20hosted%20Maldives%20President%20Mohamed%20Muizzu%20to%20a%20bilateral%20meet%20this%20afternoon%3B%20visuals%20of%20the%20two%20leaders%20clasping%20hands%20and%20smiling%20broadly%20-%20after%20a%20ceremonial%20welcome%20by%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20at%20Raj%20Bhavan%20-%20were%20posted%20by%20news%20agency%20ANI%20and%20widely%20shared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20his%20part%20Mr%20Muizzu%20once%20again%20pitched%20for%20the%20large-scale%20return%20of%20Indian%20tourists%20to%20the%20Maldives%3B%20tourism%20is%20the%20island%20nation's%20biggest%20source%20of%20revenue%20and%20this%20took%20a%20hit%20last%20year%20after%20Indian%20tourists%20cancelled%20reservations%20to%20protest%20three%20Maldivian%20minister's%20comment%20about%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%20The%20Maldives%20Foreign%20Ministry%20had%20distanced%20itself%20from%20the%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maldivian%20leader%20said%20he%20also%20hopes%20to%20conclude%20a%20free%20trade%20agreement%20with%20India%2C%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20increasing%20investment%20in%20his%20country.%20The%20Indian%20government%20has%20already%20helped%20set%20up%20a%20substantial%20drinking%20water%20and%20sewerage%20facility%20in%20the%20Maldives%20-%20this%20was%20handed%20over%20by%20Foreign%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20last%20month%20-%20and%20is%20also%20helping%20build%20road%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%20Mr%20Muizzu%20stressed%20his%20country%20would%20not%20act%20to%20undermine%20India's%20security%2C%20and%20that%20it%20views%20New%20Delhi%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bvalued%20partner%20and%20friend%26quot%3B.%20Cross-country%20cooperation%20in%20several%20fields%20-%20including%20defence%20-%20will%20%26quot%3Balways%20be%20a%20priority%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20told%20a%20leading%20English%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaldives%20would%20never%20do%20anything%20to%20undermine%20security%20of%20India.%20While%20we%20enhance%20cooperation%20with%20other%20countries%20in%20various%20sectors%2C%20we%20remain%20committed%20to%20ensuring%20our%20actions%20do%20not%20compromise%20the%20security%20and%20stability%20of%20our%20region...%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20The%20Times%20of%20India%20in%20an%20extensive%20interview%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20Mr%20Muizzu's%20first%20bilateral%20visit%20and%20the%20comments%20reflect%20growing%20bonhomie%20after%20a%20months-long%20diplomatic%20stand-off%20last%20year%2C%20over%20three%20Maldivian%20ministers'%20comments%20about%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20after%20a%20social%20media%20post%20about%20Lakshadweep%20as%20an%20alternate%20tourist%20destination%20to%20the%20Maldives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%20the%20request%20in%20May%20-%20weeks%20before%20attending%20Mr%20Modi's%20swearing-in%20ceremony%20-%20to%20remove%2090%20military%20personnel%20deployed%20to%20three%20aviation%20platforms%20gifted%20by%20India%20-%20also%20raised%20eyebrows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20accepted%20the%20request%20and%20replaced%20military%20personnel%20with%20%26quot%3Bcompetent%20technical%26quot%3B%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ejection%20of%20Indian%20military%20personnel%20and%20an%20'India%20Out'%20agenda%20was%20seen%20as%20one%20of%20Mr%20Muizzu's%20key%20poll%20promises.%20Pressed%20on%20these%20topics%2C%20the%20Maldives%20President%20said%20he%20%26quot%3Bdid%20what%20the%20people%20of%20Maldives%20asked%20of%20me%26quot%3B%2C%20but%20stressed%20India%20remains%20a%20key%20partner%20in%20efforts%20to%20secure%20regional%20stability.%20He%20denied%20that%20his%20government%20has%20an%20'India%20out'%20agenda%20and%20said%20it%20was%20simply%20the%20case%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20people%20of%20Maldives%20do%20not%20want%20a%20foreign%20soldier%20in%20their%20country%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728290100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fii54qd8o_narendra-modi-maldives-president-mohamed-muizzu-modi-muizzu_625x300_10_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-has-always-been-first-responder-pm-modi-meets-maldives-president-muizzu-6734473%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20Monday%20underlined%20New%20Delhi's%20position%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bclose%20friend%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20Maldives%20and%20emphasised%20his%20government's%20readiness%20to%20respond%20to%20medical%20and%20economic%20emergencies%20as%20part%20of%20its%20'neighbourhood%20first'%20foreign%20policy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-has-always-been-first-responder-pm-modi-meets-maldives-president-muizzu-6734473%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BRumours%20Unfounded%26quot%3B%3A%20Ratan%20Tata%20Says