0landing%20techniques%20will%20be%20temporarily%20stopped%2C%20as%20part%20of%20the%20safety%20measures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20safety%20measures%20will%20affect%20auto-landing%20operations%2C%20especially%20during%20winter%20when%20low-visibility%20landings%20are%20more%20common.%20No%20landings%20in%20low%20visibility%2Ffog%20or%20poor%20weather%20will%20be%20possible%20until%20the%20issue%20is%20resolved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20directly%20impacts%20Air%20India%20Express%2C%20Akasa%2C%20SpiceJet%2C%20and%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20which%20operate%20different%20variants%20of%20the%20Boeing%20737%20jetliner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoeing%20737%20is%20a%20legacy%20aircraft%20widely%20operated%20in%20India.%20It%20is%20part%20of%20the%20VIP%20squadron%20and%20even%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20the%20President%20fly%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DGCA%20statement%20said%20it%20has%20taken%20into%20cognizance%20of%20a%20report%20by%20the%20US%20National%20Transportation%20Safety%20Board%20that%20highlighted%20safety%20concerns%20involving%20Boeing%20737%20airplanes%20equipped%20with%20a%20certain%20type%20of%20rudder%20control%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NTSB%20had%20Thursday%20issued%20safety%20recommendations%20about%20the%20potential%20risk%20of%20jammed%20rudder%20controls%20on%20some%20737%20aircraft.%20The%20report%20followed%20a%20February%20incident%20in%20which%20rudder%20pedals%20were%20jammed%20in%20the%20neutral%20position%20on%20a%20737%20Max%208%20aircraft%20while%20landing%20in%20Newark.%20There%20were%20no%20injuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoeing%20is%20yet%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728289080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F6hi2jqr_air-india-express_625x300_07_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faviation-watchdogs-caution-to-airlines-operating-boeing-737-jets-6734271%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Indian%20aviati