reet%20Journal%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20then%20Chief%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20a%20bizarre%20explanation%3A%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EIf%20a%20mother%20tells%20her%20daughter%20to%20have%20milk%2C%20they'll%20have%20a%20fight.%20She'll%20tell%20her%20mother%2C%20'I%20won't%20drink%20milk.%20I'll%20get%20fat.'%20They%20have%20money%20but%20she's%20beauty%20conscious%2C%20she's%20not%20health%20conscious.%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20been%20a%20decade%20since%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20became%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%20The%20same%20behavioural%20pattern%20persists.%20Is%20this%20what%20medical%20professionals%20refer%20to%20as%20AVPD%20(Avoidant%20Personality%20Disorder)%20-%20a%20condition%20where%20a%20person%20is%20extremely%20sensitive%20to%20criticism%3F%20Are%20you%20surprised%20then%20that%20in%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20government's%20'100-day%20agenda'%20and%20the%20Finance%20Minister's%20Budget%20Speech%2C%20the%20words%20%26quot%3Bhunger%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bnutrition%26quot%3B%20were%20not%20mentioned%20even%20once!%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20the%20harsh%20realities%3A%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E2%97%8F%C2%A0%C2%A0%20%C2%A0One%20out%20of%20three%20of%20the%20world's%20malnourished%20children%20live%20in%20India.%20The%20percentage%20of%20people%20suffering%20from%20chronic%20hunger%20rose%20from%2010%25%20in%202014-16%20to%20almost%2014%25%20in%202021-23%20-%20an%20increase%20of%20five%20crore%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%97%8F%C2%A0%C2%A0%20%C2%A0Income%20inequality%2C%20inflation%2C%20and%20unemployment%20have%20left%2070%25%20of%20Indians%20unable%20to%20afford%20a%20basic%2C%20healthy%20diet.%20A%20home-cooked%20veg-thali%20costs%208%25%20more%20year%20on%20year.%20Annually%2C%2017%20lakh%20Indians%20die%20from%20diseases%20related%20to%20insufficient%20food%20intake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%97%8F%C2%A0%C2%A0%20%C2%A0The%20Global%20Nutrition%20Report%202024%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BNo%20progress%20has%20been%20made%20by%20India%20towards%20achieving%20the%20target%20of%20reducing%20anaemia%20among%20women%20of%20reproductive%20age.%20Meanwhile%2C%20there%20is%20insufficient%20data%20to%20assess%20the%20progress%20that%20India%20has%20made%20towards%20achieving%20the%20low%20birth%20weight%20target%2C%20nor%20is%20there%20adequate%20prevalence%20data.%20India%20has%20made%20no%20progress%20towards%20achieving%20the%20target%20for%20wasting%2C%20with%2017%25%20of%20children%20under%205%20years%20of%20age%20affected.%20This%20is%20higher%20than%20the%20average%20for%20the%20Asia%20region%20and%20among%20the%20highest%20in%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%97%8F%C2%A0%C2%A0%20%C2%A0Even%20if%20the%20Indian%20government%20disputes%20the%20findings%20of%20a%20report%20prepared%20by%20five%20international%20organisations%2C%20its%20own%20National%20Family%20Health%20Survey%20paints%20a%20disturbing%20picture%20of%20the%20country's%20nutrition%20status%3A%2032%25%20children%20are%20underweight%2C%2035%25%20children%20are%20stunted%2C%20and%2059%25%20children%20under%20the%20age%20of%20five%20years%2C%20and%2053%25%20women%20are%20anaemic.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%97%8F%C2%A0%C2%A0%20%C2%A0The%20state%20that%20has%20a%20massive%20cricket%20stadium%20named%20after%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20is%20ranked%20among%20the%20bottom%20four%20states%20in%20the%20country%20in%20tackling%20hunger.%20(Source%3A%20NITI%20Aayog's%202023-24%20report)%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%97%8F%C2%A0%C2%A0%20%C2%A0Varanasi%2C%20the%20constituency%20Narendra%20Modi%20represents%20in%20Parliament%2C%20recorded%20a%2013%25%20prevalence%20of%20children%20with%20Severe%20Acute%20Malnutrition%20(SAM).%20(Source%3A%20National%20Family%20Health%20Survey)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%97%8F%C2%A0%C2%A0%20%C2%A0Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Gujarat%20have%20topped%20the%20list%20for%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20children%20under%20five%20years%20with%20medical%20complications%20in%20Nutrition%20Rehabilitation%20Centres.%20Sadly%2C%20these%20numbers%20have%20doubled%20in%20the%20last%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%97%8F%C2%A0%C2%A0%20%C2%A0More%20than%2010%20lakh%20people%20suffer%20from%20sickle%20cell%20anaemia%2C%20a%20disease%20primarily%20prevalent%20in%20tribal%20populations%2C%20largely%20due%20to%20malnutrition.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%97%8F%C2%A0%C2%A0%20%C2%A014%20lakh%20children%20are%20severely%20malnourished%20in%20the%20country%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Union%20government's%20Poshan%20Tracker.%20These%20children%20are%20also%20nine%20times%20more%20likely%20to%20die%20due%20to%20their%20weakened%20immune%20system.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%97%8F%C2%A0%C2%A0%20%C2%A0Over%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20the%20reduction%20in%20food%20subsidies%20has%20created%20a%20ripple%20effect%20on%20nutritional%20security%20across%20the%20country.%20The%20Ministry%20of%20Women%20and%20Child%20Development%20saw%20a%20marginal%202.5%25%20increase%20in%20the%202024-25%20Union%20Budget.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20revolutionary%20Integrated%20Child%20Development%20Scheme%20(ICDS)%20and%20the%20mid-day%20meal%20programme%20faced%20a%20budget%20cut%20of%202%25%2C%20jeopardising%20the%20nutritional%20support%20for%20millions%20of%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20this%20year%2C%20one%20of%20Narendra%20Modi's%20colleagues%20in%20the%20Cabinet%2C%20the%20former%20Minister%20of%20Women%20and%20Child%20Development%2C%20declared%2C%20%26quot%3BGovernance%20is%20a%20continuous%20effort.%20Health%20and%20nutrition%20are%20left%20for%20states%20to%20deliver.%26quot%3B%20Seriously!%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20tops%20the%20list%20in%20zero-food%20children.%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20allocates%20a%20meagre%20Rs%2012%20daily%20to%20tackle%20malnutrition.%20An%20elderly%20disabled%20woman%20crawls%20in%20Odisha%20to%20collect%20her%20pension%20and%20rations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20will%20this%20government%20step%20out%