20it%2C%20but%20we%20can't%20rush%20in%20changing%20our%20approach.%26quot%3B%20Shanto%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20their%20powerplay%20approach%20needs%20to%20be%20reviewed%20with%20the%20opening%20stands%20having%20contributed%20only%2069%20runs%20in%20the%20last%20eight%20innings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPowerplay%20is%20definitely%20a%20worry.%20The%20approach%20we%20talked%20about%20(before%20the%20game)%2C%20it%20will%20be%20successful%20if%20we%20make%20a%20good%20start%20with%20the%20bat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20keep%20the%20wickets%20in%20the%20first%20six%20overs%2C%20and%20score%20runs%20in%20those.%20Otherwise%20those%20coming%20in%20next%2C%20it%20becomes%20too%20challenging%20for%20them.%20We%20have%20struggled%20in%20the%20powerplay.%20Those%20batting%20in%20the%20power%20play%20must%20take%20more%20responsibility%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20southpaw.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERookier%20Indian%20pacer%20Mayank%20Yadav%20made%20a%20promising%20debut%20on%20Sunday%2C%20generating%20speeds%20close%20to%20150kmph%20in%20his%20first%20competitive%20game%20in%20five%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20hurried%20the%20batters%20but%20Shanto%20said%20they%20are%20used%20to%20facing%20such%20speed%20in%20the%20nets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20some%20similar%20fast%20bowlers%20in%20the%20nets.%20I%20don't%20think%20we%20were%20too%20worried%20about%20(Mayank%20Yadav).%20But%20he%20is%20a%20good%20bowler%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728275640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fn4np4728_shanto-bcci_625x300_07_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-bangladesh-2024%2Fdont-know-how-to-score-180-runs-skipper-najmul-hossain-shanto-throws-bangladesh-under-the-bus-6733201%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bangladesh%20were%20bowled%20out%20for%20127%20runs%20in%20the%20first%20T20I%20of%20the%203-match%20series%20against%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A53%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-bangladesh-2024%2Fdont-know-how-to-score-180-runs-skipper-najmul-hossain-shanto-throws-bangladesh-under-the-bus-6733201%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Doctor%20Visited%20His%20Gaza%20Hometown%20A%20Week%20Before%20October%207.%20He%20Never%20Left%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20been%20a%20year%20since%20the%20war%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%20erupted%2C%20a%20conflict%20that%20has%20brought%20unspeakable%20devastation%20to%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%20The%20days%20since%20October%207%20have%20stretched%20into%20months%20of%20relentless%20bombings%2C%20displacement%2C%20and%20desperation.%20For%20the%20people%20living%20in%20Gaza%2C%20the%20conflict%20has%20stripped%20them%20of%20their%20homes%2C%20their%20loved%20ones%2C%20and%20their%20sense%20of%20normalcy.%20It%20is%20not%20just%20buildings%20that%20have%20crumbled%2C%20but%20entire%20lives%20-%20careers%2C%20dreams%2C%20families%20-%20torn%20apart%20by%20the%20ravages%20of%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20numbers%20tell%20only%20part%20of%20the%20story.%20Behind%20each%20statistic%20is%20a%20personal%20tragedy.%20Homes%20are%20now%20rubble%2C%20hospitals%20are%20overwhelmed%2C%20and%20the%20world%20seems%20to%20look%20on%20helplessly%2C%20watching%20as%20the%20conflict%20deepens.%20The%20war%20has%20displaced%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%2C%20turning%20vibrant%20communities%20into%20mere%20shadows%20of%20their%20former%20selves.%20For%20the%20survivors%2C%20daily%20life%20is%20a%20continuous%20struggle%2C%20and%20yet%20within%20that%20struggle%2C%20there%20are%20those%20who%20push%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20such%20individual%20is%20Dr%20Khaled%20Alshawwa%2C%20a%2031-year-old%20surgeon%20from%20Gaza%20City.%20Khaled%2C%20like%20many%20in%20his%20community%2C%20never%20planned%20to%20be%20on%20the%20frontlines%20of%20a%20humanitarian%20crisis.%20Just%20a%20week%20before%20the%20war%2C%20he%20had%20completed%20his%20surgical%20training%20at%20Almakassed%20Hospital%20in%20Jerusalem%2C%20a%20prestigious%20medical%20institution.%20He%20had%20returned%20to%20Gaza%20for%20what%20was%20meant%20to%20be%20a%20brief%20family%20visit-just%20a%20few%20days%20to%20reconnect%20with%20loved%20ones%20before%20continuing%20his%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F41i3rc68_gaza-doctor-_625x300_06_October_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20then%20the%20war%20began%2C%20and%20everything%20changed.%20In%20an%20instant%2C%20Khaled%20found%20himself%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20one%20of%20the%20most%20brutal%20conflicts%20Gaza%20has%20seen%2C%20unable%20to%20leave%2C%20compelled%20to%20stay%20and%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20immediate%20aftermath%20was%20chaos%2C%26quot%3B%20Khaled%20recalls.%20%26quot%3BWe%20faced%20an%20overwhelming%20influx%20of%20severely%20injured%20patients%20with%20limited%20medical%20supplies%20and%20infrastructure.%20This%20was%20much%20aggregated%20and%20intensified%20after%20the%20destruction%20of%20many%20hospitals.%20As%20a%20doctor%2C%20I%20have%20to%20prioritise%20cases%2C%20often%20making%20difficult%20decisions%20with%20minimal%20resources.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhaled%2C%20a%20surgeon%20trained%20for%20the%20most%20complex%20procedures%2C%20was%20forced%20to%20make%20rapid%2C%20agonising%20decisions%20with%20almost%20no%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLife%20has%20drastically%20changed.%20I%20am%20constantly%20navigating%20between%20being%20a%20surgeon%2C%20managing%20medical%20points%2C%20struggling%20to%20provide%20basic%20daily%20needs%20to%20me%20and%20my%20family%20like%20fresh%20water%2C%20food%20and%20a%20place%20to%20stay%20in%20amidst%20severe%20shortages%20of%20resources%20and%20ongoing%20bombings%2C%26quot%3B%20Khaled%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20injuries%20that%20filled%20the%20hospitals%20were%20devastating%3A%20shrapnel%20wounds%2C%20blast%20injuries%2C%20complex%20fractures%2C%20severe%20burns%2C%20and%20traumatic%20amputations.%20%26quot%3BMany%20of%20the%20injuries%20involve%20multiple%20body%20parts%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explains%2C%20requiring%20teams%20of%20surgeons%20working%20in%20tandem.%20But%20with%20a%20healthcare%20system%20on%20the%20brink%20of%20collapse%2C%20they%20don't%20have%20the%20luxury%20of%20specialisation.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20stretched%20beyond%20belief.%20A%20surgeon%20might%20have%20to%20handle%20trauma%2C%20pediatric%20surgery%2C%20even%20urology%2C%20and%20vascular%20procedures%2C%20all%20at%20once.%20It%20is%20exhausting%2C%20physically%20and%20mentally.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20was%20made%20worse%20by%20the%20fact%20that%20medical%20supplies%20are%20running%20low.%20Basic%20necessities%20-%20anaesthetics%2C%20sutures%2C%20bandages%2C%20antibiotics%20-%20are%20in%20short%20supply.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20improvise%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BIn%20some%20cases%2C%20we%20had%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20turn%20to%20telemedicine%2C%20relying%20on%20colleagues%20abroad%20for%20guidance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chaos%20of%20the%20war%20meant%20that%20Khaled's%20life%20is%20in%20constant%20motion.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20moved%20seven%20times%20since%20the%20war%20began%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says%2C%20each%20relocation%20a%20desperate%20attempt%20to%20keep%20his%20family%20safe.%20His%20base%20of%20operations%20has%20also%20shifted%20as%20the%20conflict%20ebbs%20and%20flows.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20volunteered%20at%20almost%20every%20hospital%20in%20Gaza%20City%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explains%2C%20as%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20war%20has%20required%20him%20to%20be%20flexible.%20%26quot%3BWherever%20I%20go%2C%20I%20try%20to%20offer%20what%20little%20help%20I%20can.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F5kkd5dto_gaza-doctor-_625x300_06_October_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Khaled%2C%20each%20new%20base%20brings%20with%20it%20a%20fresh%20set%20of%20challenges.%20He%20describes%20the%20scenes%20with%20stark%20clarity%20-%20overcrowded%20refugee%20camps%2C%20where%20families%20huddle%20together%20in%20makeshift%20shelters%2C%20trying%20to%20stay%20alive%20amidst%20airstrikes%20from%20Israel.%20%26quot%3BInfection%20control%20is%20nearly%20impossible%20in%20these%20conditions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says%2C%20pointing%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20sanitation%20and%20clean%20water.%20Overcrowding%20in%20the%20camps%20has%20led%20to%20the%20rapid%20spread%20of%20disease.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20seeing%20infections%20in%20open%20wounds%2C%20as%20well%20as%20dermatological%20diseases%20in%20previously%20healthy%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20camps%2C%20Khaled%20notes%2C%20are%20where%20the%20most%20vulnerable-women%20and%20children-are%20suffering%20the%20most.%20%26quot%3BMaternity%20and%20pediatric%20care%20are%20severely%20impacted%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BMany%20women%20are%20giving%20birth%20in%20unsafe%20environments%2C%20and%20children%20are%20missing%20out%20on%20basic%20healthcare.%26quot%3B%20Immunisation%20programs%2C%20vital%20to%20protecting%20children%20from%20preventable%20diseases%2C%20have%20also%20been%20disrupted.%20Khaled%20himself%20was%20involved%20in%20a%20recent%20polio%20vaccination%20campaign%20organised%20by%20the%20Palestine%20Red%20Crescent%20Society.%20Despite%20the%20overwhelming%20challenges%2C%20including%20maintaining%20cold%20chains%20for%20vaccines%20in%20areas%20with%20no%20electricity%2C%20the%20team%20managed%20to%20vaccinate%20over%20120%2C000%20children%20under%20the%20age%20of%20ten%20in%20North%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20is%20not%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20strain%20on%20Gaza's%20healthcare%20system%20is%20unprecedented%2C%20and%20the%20long-term%20impact%20of%20the%20war%20on%20public%20health%20is%20staggering.%20%26quot%3BThe%20magnitude%20of%20disability%20we%20are%20witnessing%20is%20terrifying%2C%26quot%3B%20Khaled%20says.%20The%20rise%20in%20amputations%2C%20spinal%20injuries%2C%20and%20traumatic%20brain%20damage%20will%20have%20consequences%20that%20last%20for%20decades.%20%26quot%3BThese%20are%20injuries%20that%20will%20require%20years%2C%20if%20not%20a%20lifetime%2C%20of%20care%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20warns.%20%26quot%3BThe%20healthcare%20system%20simply%20isn't%20equipped%20to%20deal%20with%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20many%20in%20Gaza%2C%20Khaled's%20personal%20losses%20are%20intertwined%20with%20the%20collective%20grief%20of%20his%20people.%20%26quot%3BI%20lost%20my%20mother%20in%20a%20bombing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20revealed.%20In%20addition%20to%20his%20mother%2C%20he%20has%20lost%20his%20home%20and%20many%20close%20friends.%20But%20despite%20this%20immense%20personal%20loss%2C%20Khaled%20has%20remained%20resolute.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20tough%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20admits.%20%26quot%3BPsychologically%2C%20it's%20very%20hard.%20The%20constant%20pressure%2C%20the%20loss%2C%20the%20fear%20for%20your%20family%20-%20it%20takes%20a%20toll.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20yet%2C%20like%20so%20many%20others%20in%20Gaza%2C%20Khaled%20continues%20to%20move%20forward.%20%26quot%3BStaying%20focused%20on%20helping%20others%20is%20what%20keeps%20me%20going%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says%2C%20though%20there%20are%20moments%20when%20the%20weight%20of%20it%20all%20feels%20unbearable.%20%26quot%3BEvery%20day%20is%20a%20struggle%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20admits.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20can't%20give%20up%2C%20not%20when%20there%20are%20so%20many%20people%20depending%20on%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20war%20in%20Gaza%20is%20not%20happening%20in%20isolation.%20The%20Israeli-Hamas%20conflict%20has%20drawn%20in%20international%20players%2C%20with%20each%20new%20development%20bringing%20the%20risk%20of%20a%20broader%20regional%20conflict.%20In%20Lebanon%2C%20Israeli%20airstrikes%20have%20intensified%2C%20killing%20hundreds.%20Hezbollah%2C%20a%20militant%20group%20backed%20by%20Iran%2C%20has%20escalated%20its%20exchanges%20with%20Israel%2C%20meaning%20that%20the%20war%20has%20extended%20far%20beyond%20Gaza's%20borders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Europe%2C%20the%20conflict%20has%20sparked%20a%20political%20backlash.%20Countries%20like%20Spain%20and%20Ireland%20have%20recognised%20the%20State%20of%20Palestine%20in%20defiance%20of%20Israeli%20opposition.%20The%20United%20States%20on%20the%20other%20hand%20continues%20to%20provide%20Israel%20with%20military%20and%20financial%20support%2C%20most%20recently%20approving%20an%20%248.7%20billion%20aid%20package.%20For%20Palestinians%20like%20Khaled%2C%20international%20aid%20is%20critical%20to%20the%20survival%20of%20Gaza's%20healthcare%20system%2C%20yet%20the%20future%20of%20that%20support%20remains%20uncertain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20Nations%20estimates%20that%20nearly%2080%2C000%20homes%20have%20been%20destroyed%2C%20and%20it%20could%20take%20decades%20to%20rebuild%20the%20city.%20Khaled%20agrees.%20%26quot%3BIt%20will%20take%20years%2C%20maybe%20even%20decades%2C%20to%20get%20Gaza's%20health%20infrastructure%20back%20on%20track%2C%26quot%3B%20Khaled%20says.%20%26quot%3BWithout%20substantial%20international%20aid%2C%20the%20recovery%20will%20be%20slow%2C%20and%20people%20will%20continue%20to%20suffer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20road%20to%20recovery%20is%20long%2C