r%20Sergey%20Brin%20have%20established%20family%20offices%20in%20the%20city-state.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freliance-industries-mukesh-ambani-new-family-office-singapore-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMukesh%20Ambani%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Asia's%20richest%20man%2C%20also%20expanded%20his%20wealth%20management%20operations%20to%20Singapore%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20spoke%20to%20three%20recruiters%20for%20family%20offices%2C%20two%20of%20whom%20are%20based%20in%20Singapore%2C%20to%20find%20out%20which%20traits%20give%20a%20candidate%20the%20best%20shot%20of%20landing%20a%20job%20in%20a%20family%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22250f7d12-74d8-46a4-828f-083dfef98f32%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Jack%20of%20all%20trades%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20many%20corporate%20jobs'%20clearly-defined%20responsibilities%2C%20family%20office%20staff%20%E2%80%94%20even%20executives%20%E2%80%94%20juggle%20a%20lot%2C%20said%20Paul%20Westall%2C%20the%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ecofounder%20of%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAgreus%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20chief%20investment%20officer%20of%20Goldman%20Sachs%20might%20not%20fit%20nicely%20into%20a%20family%20office%20because%2C%20at%20Goldman%2C%20they%20might%20have%2010%20analysts%20and%20two%20assistants%2C%20while%20in%20a%20family%20office%2C%20they%20do%20all%20the%20analysis%20and%20book%20their%20flights%2C%26quot%3B%20Westall%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJimmy%20Soh%2C%20a%20consultant%20at%20recruitment%20firm%20AP%20Executive%2C%20stressed%20the%20need%20to%20wear%20multiple%20hats%20and%20cultivate%20multiple%20specializations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20only%20do%20you%20have%20to%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ebe%20an%20investment%20manager%2C%20but%20you%20also%20have%20to%20be%20a%20family%20council%20and%20any%20additional%20roles%20coming%20in%20like%20a%20concierge%20service%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Soh.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%