firms%2C%26quot%3B%20Soh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Asia%2C%20many%20family%20offices%20are%20still%20developing%20and%20roles%20are%20less%20defined%20than%20in%20Europe%20or%20the%20US.%20Candidates%20must%20often%20be%20willing%20to%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flessons-hint-ceo-learned-doing-dirty-work-leader-2021-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eget%20their%20hands%20dirty%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20work%20long%20hours%20for%20seven%20days%20a%20week%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Pierre%20Pineau%2C%20head%20of%20Agreus%20Group's%20Singapore%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAsian%20families%2C%20in%20general%2C%20expect%20you%20to%20be%20available%2024%2F7%2C%20and%20that's%20not%20for%20everyone%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Pineau.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20about%20yourself.%20It's%20about%20what's%20best%20for%20the%20family%20office.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20jobs%20can%20also%20require%20independence.%20Pineau%20said%20that%20in%20Asia's%20emerging%20markets%2C%20employees%20often%20work%20independently%20in%20one%20location%20while%20the%20family's%20main%20office%20is%20in%20another%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWestall%20said%20flexibility%20is%20key.%20He%20once%20hired%20a%20CIO%20whose%20job%20description%20included%20overseeing%20a%20family's%20investment%20in%20purebred%20racehorses.%20A%20top%20candidate%20%E2%80%94%20a%20former%20banker%20%E2%80%94%20had%20no%20experience%20in%20horses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225184%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Horse%20Racing%20Canada%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66fe40d69e0c5c2eeeea3f25%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223456%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFamily%20office%20staff%20need%20to%20learn%20on%20the%20fly%20%E2%80%94%20even%20about%20racehorses.%3Cp%3EMike%20Campbell%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20then%20he%20got%20this%20job%20and%20rolled%20with%20it%20because%20he%20had%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Westall.%20%26quot%3BKey%20people%20that%20last%20a%20long%20time%20in%20family%20offices%20build%20trust%20because%20when%20there's%20an%20issue%2C%20they%20resolve%20it%20with%20ideas%20from%20outside%20the%20box.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221bba166f-2ad4-4b9b-8108-ea6b7b35d0a4%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Managing%20multiple%20family%20members%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20family%20offices%2C%20technical%20brilliance%20alone%20isn't%20enough%20to%20secure%20a%20role.%20Working%20closely%20for%20one%20family%20means%20managing%20wealth%20and%20relationships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20main%20attributes%20family%20offices%20need%20is%20emotional%20intelligence%20%E2%80%94%20someone%20who%20can%20work%20with%20multiple%20people%20of%20different%20levels%2C%20from%20the%20son%20who's%2016%20and%20you%20need%20to%20explain%20certain%20decisions%20to%20him%2C%20to%20the%20wife%2C%20and%20the%20granddad%2C%26quot%3B%20Agreus%20Group's%20Westall%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECandidates%20must%20also%20have%20the%20communication%20skills%20to%20navigate%20the%20dynamics%20and%20demands%20of%20different%20family%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20are%20presenting%20your%20work%20to%20people%20who%20might%20not%20be%20particularly%20financially%20savvy%2C%20unlike%20your%20peers%20at%20a%20bank%2C%26quot%3B%20Westall%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAP%20Executive's%20Soh%20said%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bintangibles%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20like%20interpersonal%20compatibility%20and%20standout%20personality%20traits%E2%80%94%20often%20make%20or%20break%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20might%20be%20extremely%20brilliant%2C%20but%20you%20might%20be%20a%20very%20hard%20person%20to%20work%20with%20or%20have%20some%20idiosyncrasies%20that%20might%20not%20gel%20well%20with%20the%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Soh.%20%26quot%3BIt%20comes%20down%20to%20your%20personality.%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20hired%20often%20hinges%20on%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonality-hires-bring-soft-skills-to-work-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20personality%20fit%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20Westall.%20Families%20might%20reject%20candidates%20for%20small%20details%20like%20how%20they%20walk%20or%20dress%20%E2%80%94%20but%20others%20are%20open%20to%20unconventional%20hires.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWestall%20shared%20a%20story%20of%20a%20family%20office%20executive%20who%20started%20as%20a%20cleaner%20while%20he%20was%20in%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efilm%20school.%20He%20helped%20the%20family%20with%20a%20script%20they%20were%20writing%20and%20was%20eventually%20hired%20to%20oversee%20investments%20in%20the%20family's%20film%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSometimes%20they%20are%20not%20always%20looking%20for%20someone%20with%20obvious%20experience%2C%20but%20someone%20who%20could%20add%20value%20in%20that%20family%20office%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Westall.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20an%20unusual%20story%2C%20but%20there%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eare%20some%20bizarre%20ways%20people%20can%20get%20into%20family%20offices.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20working%20with%20or%20for%20high-net-worth%20individuals%3F%20Email%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Alwee%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Elwee%40insider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-job-family-office-personality-recruiters-singapore-asia-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728259202000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66fd4c347de5c8fd483492a6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-job-family-office-personalit