f%20%26quot%3Bunprecedented%20savagery%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20a%2036-year-old%20football%20player%2C%20Nessim%20Ramdane%2C%20was%20shot%20and%20killed%20%26quot%3Bin%20cold%20blood%26quot%3B%20by%20a%2014-year-old%20in%20a%20case%20linked%20to%20Wednesday's%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20latest%20cases%20mean%20that%20the%20number%20of%20drug-related%20killings%20in%20Marseille%20has%20risen%20to%2017%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarseille's%20drug%20lords%20have%20been%20recruiting%20foot%20soldiers%20with%20ads%20on%20social%20media%2C%20%26quot%3Boutsourcing%26quot%3B%20street%20dealing%20to%20youngsters%20known%20as%20%26quot%3Bjobbeurs%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBessone%20said%20on%20Sunday%20that%20now%20young%20boys%20were%20responding%20to%20ads%20not%20only%20to%20sell%20cannabis%20resin%20but%20also%20to%20kill%20%26quot%3Bwithout%20any%20remorse%20or%20reflection%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20teenager%20had%20been%20hired%20via%20social%20networks%20by%20a%2023-year-old%20prisoner%20to%20intimidate%20a%20competitor%20by%20setting%20fire%20to%20his%20door%2C%20the%20prosecutor%20said%2C%20adding%20the%20youth%20had%20been%20promised%202%2C000%20euros.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20detainee%20of%20the%20Luynes%20prison%20south%20of%20Aix-en-Provence%20had%20described%20himself%20as%20a%20member%20of%20DZ%20Mafia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShot%20in%20the%20head%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20mission%2C%20the%20teenager%20was%20spotted%20by%20members%20of%20a%20rival%20gang%20who%20searched%20him%20and%20discovered%20that%20he%20was%20carrying%20a%20gun.%20To%20punish%20the%20minor%2C%20they%20repeatedly%20stabbed%20him%20then%20set%20him%20on%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20was%20stabbed%2050%20times%20and%20taken%20to%20the%20Fonscolombes%20housing%20estate%2C%20where%2C%20according%20to%20the%20results%20of%20the%20autopsy%2C%20he%20was%20burned%