%22%20height%3D%5C%2275%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPooja%20Bangad%2C%20the%20co-founder%20of%20%3Cem%3ESheWork.in%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20platform%20that%20connects%20women%20with%20flexible%20work%20opportunities%20in%20the%20tech%20industry%20%E2%80%94%20remembers%20what%20got%20her%20started%20as%20an%20entrepreneur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CComing%20from%20a%20traditional%20joint%20family%2C%20I%20am%20a%20first-generation%20female%20entrepreneur.%20After%20my%20graduation%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20work%20and%20travel%20overseas.%20I%20got%20a%20good%20opportunity%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F202915%2Fjbs-handale-world-greatest-scientist-genetics-citizenship-united-kingdom-india-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUnited%20Kingdom%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20work%20and%20study%2C%20but%20my%20family%20did%20not%20allow%20me%20to%20go.%20I%20remember%20my%20relatives%20asking%20me%2C%20%E2%80%98What%20if%20you%20get%20a%20high-paying%20job%3F%20How%20will%20we%20find%20a%20suitable%20marriage%20proposal%20for%20you%3F%E2%80%99%20I%20also%20remember%20people%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%98What%20will%20you%20do%20with%20so%20much%20education%E2%80%99.%20%5BAfter%20listening%20to%20such%20comments%5D%20I%20decided%20to%20be%20independent%20and%20do%20something%20on%20my%20own%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Pooja%2C%20a%20native%20of%20Pune%2C%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20a%20master%E2%80%99s%20degree%20in%20computer%20science%2C%20she%20joined%20a%20reputed%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F307590%2Festher-foundation-fellowship-programme-helping-bahujan-women-find-jobs-in-accenture-tcs-genpact%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emultinational%20company%20%3C%2Fa%3E(MNC).%20What%20she%20witnessed%20there%20would%20go%20on%20to%20determine%20her%20professional%20choices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20very%20junior%20employee%20of%20an%20MNC%2C%20I%20remember%20the%20struggle%20my%20female%20manager%20went%20through%20for%20her%20promotions%20and%20on-site%20opportunities.%20Working%20at%20that%20company%20for%20two%20or%20three%20years%2C%20I%20always%20saw%20her%20professional%20ambitions%20stifled%20compared%20to%20other%20male%20managers%20in%20the%20company%20despite%20her%20experience%20and%20skills%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CShe%20never%20got%20on-site%20opportunities%20that%20other%20male%20managers%20had%20because%20she%20was%20judged%20for%20having%20two%20children.%20Nobody%20asked%20her%20whether%20her%20family%20was%20flexible%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20working%20on-site.%20She%20would%20work%20round%20the%20clock%2C%20support%20every%20member%20of%20her%20team%2C%20and%20even%20support%20her%20colleagues%20working%20on-site%20even%20though%20that%20opportunity%20was%20denied%20to%20her.%20I%20vividly%20remember%20feeling%20very%20bad%20for%20her.%20I%20desperately%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20for%20her%20but%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20because%20I%20was%20still%20a%20very%20junior%20employee%20with%20no%20voice%20or%20power%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20college%2C%20however%2C%20she%20kept%20in%20touch%20with%20her%20friend%20and%20batchmate%20Tejas%20Kulkarni%2C%20who%20is%20now%20the%20CEO%20of%20%3Cem%3ESheWork.in%3C%2Fem%3E.%20As%20Pooja%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20our%20many%20discussions%2C%20Tejas%20and%20I%20always%20envisioned%20wanting%20to%20do%20something%20for%20women%20working%20in%20the%20tech%20industry.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20Pooja%20and%20Tejas%20quit%20their%20respective%20jobs%20at%20different%20MNCs%20and%20started%20their%20software%20company%20called%20Telemerge%20IT%20Services%20Pvt%20Ltd%20alongside%20Pune-based%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F356672%2Fenmasse-epic-stories-video-contest-entrepreneurial-households-startups-businesses-investors-small-town-rural-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eentrepreneur%20%3C%2Fa%3ETushar%20Kulkarni%20and%20made%20their%20foray%20into%20the%20tech%20industry.%20At%20the%20outset%2C%20they%20established%20an%20informal%20rule%20that%20they%20would%20give%20more%20opportunities%20to%20women%20in%20their%20company%20to%20identify%20how%20it%20goes%2C%20before%20solving%20this%20problem%20for%20bigger%20tech%20companies%20in%20India.%20Suffice%20it%20to%20say%20that%20they%20encountered%20different%20challenges%20when%20it%20came%20to%20hiring%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20running%20Telemerge%2C%20they%20learnt%20that%20women%20looking%20to%20rejoin%20the%20workforce%20after%20a%20sabbatical%20or%20maternity%20leave%20were%20hesitant%20to%20get%20a%20job%20in%20the%20tech%20industry%20because%20they%20felt%20trapped%2C%20found%20travelling%20a%20challenge%2C%20and%20were%20struggling%20to%20strike%20a%20balance%20between%20household%20and%20office%20work.%20This%20was%20a%20problem%20they%20were%20going%20to%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSheWork.in-co-founders-1728051534.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22SheWork%20is%20helping%20women%20in%20technology%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSheWork.in-co-founders-1728051534.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSheWork.in-co-founders-1728051534-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSheWork.in-co-founders-1728051534-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%