0the%20problem%20of%20the%20lack%20of%20women%20in%20the%20tech%20industry%2C%20primarily%20in%20leadership%20or%20mid-level%20roles%20working%20on%20specified%20technologies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F323501%2Figniting-ideas-for-impact-audiobook-explores-pioneering-indian-startups%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eearlier%20conversation%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Pooja%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20trying%20to%20work%20with%20developers%20or%20people%20in%20leadership%20roles%20with%20anywhere%20between%20three%20to%2012%20years%20of%20experience.%20We%20do%20have%20plans%20in%20the%20future%20to%20help%20women%20in%20other%20industries%2C%20but%20today%2C%20our%20vision%20is%20to%20try%20and%20solve%20the%20problem%20in%20the%20tech%20industry.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20main%20focus%20is%20not%20just%20to%20solve%20the%20problem%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20talent.%20We%20also%20have%20to%20look%20at%20the%20companies%20who%20are%20going%20to%20hire%20them.%20Companies%20also%20have%20to%20trust%20women%20to%20give%20them%20a%20chance.%20Our%20focus%20lies%20in%20balancing%20their%20respective%20needs%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESheWork.in%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20focused%20on%20seamlessly%20reintegrating%20women%20with%20three%20or%20more%20years%20of%20experience%20in%20the%20tech%20industry%20back%20into%20the%20workforce%20after%20they%20had%20to%20leave%20it%20for%20reasons%20like%20marriage%2C%20relocation%2C%20childbirth%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20why%20start%20with%20women%20with%20three%20years%20of%20experience%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Pooja%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAs%20per%20our%20statistical%20findings%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20usually%20after%20three%20years%20in%20the%20workforce%20when%20women%20get%20married%20and%20relocate%20to%20where%20their%20husbands%20work.%20Once%20they%20cross%20the%20five%20or%20six-year%20experience%20threshold%2C%20we%20find%20that%20women%20have%20their%20first%20child%2C%20go%20on%20a%20maternity%20break%2C%20and%20as%20a%20result%2C%20their%20promotions%20get%20delayed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-3-1728052294.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Women%20in%20tech%20are%20being%20assisted%20by%20SheWork%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-3-1728052294.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-3-1728052294-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-3-1728052294-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-3-1728052294-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-3-1728052294-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-368860%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERepresentational%20Image%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20percentage%20of%20women%20in%20leadership%20positions%20in%20the%20tech%20industry%20is%20still%20very%20low%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Pooja%20Bangad%2C%20co-founder%20of%20SheWork.in%20(Image%20courtesy%20Shutterstock%2Finsta_photos)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20goes%20on%20to%20elaborate%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20percentage%20of%20women%20in%20leadership%20positions%20in%20the%20tech%20industry%20is%20still%20very%20low.%20Our%20focus%20is%20to%20first%20increase%20diversity%20at%20the%20leadership%20or%20C-level%20(chief-level%20jobs%20that%20are%20the%20highest%20tier%20of%20executive%20jobs%20within%20an%20organisation).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20management%20is%20liberal%20or%20open%20to%20hiring%20more%20women%20at%20their%20level%2C%20that%20is%20when%20they%20will%20guide%20their%20subordinate%20teams%20to%20hire%20more%20women.%20See%2C%20the%20market%20is%20very%20competitive.%20Nobody%20wants%20the%20other%20person%20to%20get%20ahead%20of%20them.%20This%20is%20why%20our%20journey%20to%20make%20the%20workplace%20in%20the%20tech%20industry%20more%20inclusive%20starts%20at%20the%20leadership%20level%20because%20that%E2%80%99s%20where%20they%20are%20going%20to%20promote%20and%20help%20women%20come%20back%20and%20rejoin%20the%20workforce%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESheWork.in%3C%2Fem%3E%20helps%20companies%20to%20hire%20more%20women.%20But%20this%20does%20not%20mean%20they%20ask%20companies%20to%20give%20their%20women%20applicants%20only%20remote%20working%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20asking%20them%20to%20establish%20exclusive%20policies%20to%20hire%20women%20but%20inclusive%20ones.%20Speaking%20to%20companies%2C%20we%20explain%20to%20them%20why%20it%20is%20important%20that%20they%20also%20give%20women%20an%20opportunity%20for%20the%20same%20role%20as%20they%20give%20men.%20Unlike%20days%20in%20the%20past%2C%20women%20today%20also%20travel%20and%20do%20night%20or%20second%20shifts%20while%20technology%20has%20upgraded%20and%20companies%20have%20the%20salary%20cap%20space.%20So%2C%20why%20not%20hire%20more%20capable%20women%20instead%20of%20leaving%20them%20out%3F%E2%80%9D%20says%20Pooja.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20particularly%20unique%20about%20%3Cem%3ESheWork.in%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20that%20they%20are%20focused%20on%20delivering%20well-experienced%20talent%20for%20tech%20companies%20with%20a%20turnaround%20time%20of%2024%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-