s%E2%80%99%20arches%20were%20blocked%20with%20bricks.%20When%20we%20managed%20to%20get%20into%20the%20rooms%2C%20we%20noticed%20that%20the%20doors%20and%20windows%20had%20vanished.%20We%20guessed%20that%20they%20had%20been%20vandalised%20or%20eaten%20by%20termites.%20Even%20some%20of%20the%20supporting%20beams%20were%20missing%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pallab%20recalls.%20The%20cleaning%20spree%20went%20on%20for%20years%2C%20yielding%20three%20rooms%20that%20were%20deemed%20fit%20to%20live%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20the%20family%20decided%20to%20turn%20the%20ancestral%20palace%20into%20a%20guesthouse.%20However%2C%20Pallab%20explains%20that%20the%20plan%20flopped%20as%20social%20media%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20as%20popular%20back%20then%20and%20most%20people%E2%80%99s%20first%20choice%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20a%20guest%20house.%20It%20seemed%20like%20the%2018th-century%20palace%20would%20remain%20desolate.%20Unable%20to%20watch%20their%20ancestral%20pride%20meet%20such%20a%20fate%2C%20the%20Roy%20family%20decided%20to%20rebuild%20Cossimbazar%20Palace%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F332940%2Fdevpur-royal-homestay-darbargadh-in-kutch-jadeja-family-runs-farmstay-cbse-school%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eroyal%20residence%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20would%20soon%20become%20a%20heritage%20hotel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Buckingham%20of%20India%E2%80%99%3A%20Reviving%20a%20lost%20legacy%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20heyday%2C%20the%20Cossimbazar%20Palace%20would%20have%20earned%20the%20%E2%80%98Buckingham%20of%20India%E2%80%99%20moniker.%20Explaining%20the%20comparison%2C%20Pallab%20shares%20that%20the%20palace%E2%80%99s%20functioning%20was%20in%20tune%20with%20colonial%20times%20and%20its%20practices%20mirrored%20those%20at%20Buckingham%20Palace%20in%20England.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20British%20Government%20had%20a%20system%20of%20admini